name: 【Lovelive!】Character + Official Art Style LoRA（官方畫風模組）
description:
This is a LoRA for generating images in the style of Lovelive's official artwork.

Making models takes a lot of time and hard work. If you like this LoRA, please click the like button!

v2 update:

Now you can insert the charecter's name to generate specific character(not include Superstar! and Link!Like!)

These Images were generated using AbyssOrangeMix2_SFW and some character's LoRA.

Recommended weights:

  • Recommended weights: 0.5~0.7

  • when used with character LoRA: 0.25~0.5

這是一個把生成圖像變得跟Lovelive官方畫風相似的LoRA

製作模型需要花費很多的時間和精力。如果您喜歡這個LoRA，請幫忙按一個“讚”！

v2更新:

現在你可以輸入角色的名稱去指定生成的角色(不包括星團和蓮團)！

範本圖像是使用AbyssOrangeMix2_SFW和一些角色的LoRA生成的。

建議權重：

  • 建議權重：0.5〜0.7

  • 跟角色LoRA一起使用：0.25〜0.5
